extends layout

block body
    div(class='page-header')
        h1 API Documentation

    h3 URL:
    p The base URL is:
    div(class='panel panel-default')
        div(class='panel-body')
            a http://drool.cloudapp.net/api/1.0/
    p There is only 1 allowed HTTP Method:
        a  GET
    p A wrong URL will redirect to a 404 error code page.

    div(class='page-header')
        h2 Markets:

    div(class='panel panel-default')
        div(class='panel-body')
            a GET /markets
    p Gives information about the available markets and their separate responses
    p The available market keys are:
        a(href='https://www.bitfinex.com/', target='_blank')  Bitfinex
        a(href='https://www.bitstamp.net/', target='_blank')  Bitstamp
        a(href='https://hitbtc.com/', target='_blank')  HitBTC
    h4 Parameters:
        div(class='list-group')
            a(class='list-group-item')
                h4(class='list-group-item-heading') key = "key-value"
                h5(class='list-group-item-text') Filters the content by "key"("Bitfinex", "Bitstamp"...). Must be a proper URL encoded JSON value
            a(class='list-group-item')
                h4(class='list-group-item-heading') keys = [array of "key-values"]
                h5(class='list-group-item-text') Must be a proper URL encoded JSON array value. Filters the content by the passed keys
            a(class='list-group-item')
                h4(class='list-group-item-heading') startkey = "key-value"
                h5(class='list-group-item-text') Filters the content starting with the key passed to "startkey"
            a(class='list-group-item')
                h4(class='list-group-item-heading') endkey = "key-value"
                h5(class='list-group-item-text') Displays all the content until it reaches "endkey"
            a(class='list-group-item')
                h4(class='list-group-item-heading') descending = true/false
                h5(class='list-group-item-text') Change the direction of the search
            a(class='list-group-item')
                h4(class='list-group-item-heading') skip = number of docs
                h5(class='list-group-item-text') Skip n number of documents

