    div(class='page-header')
        h2 Status:

    div(class='panel panel-default')
        div(class='panel-body')
            a GET /status

    p Gives information about the status of the API server("available" or "offline")

    h4 Example request:
    div(class='panel panel-default')
        div(class='panel-heading')
            a GET
            a
                i  http://drool.cloudapp.net/api/1.0/status
        div(class='panel-body')
            pre
                code.
                    {
                       "status":"available"
                    }